 - Built and installed both simulator channels, cloned main data into `SAVI Test`,
   and captured QA screenshot:
   `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_v5_sample_home_2026-05-04.png`.
+
+## Folder Editor Cover Image Fix
+
+- Created rollback archive:
+  `Docs/Design/FolderEditorArchive/2026-05-04-before-cover-image-editor/`.
+- Fixed Folder editor artwork semantics so choosing a photo/web image now
+  defaults to a full Folder cover background with readability overlay, while
+  the Folder symbol remains a separate icon control.
+- Selecting a new symbol no longer deletes an existing cover image.
+- Updated the preview card to render the same cover-background treatment used
+  by Home and Folders, instead of showing image artwork only as an icon.
+- Changed unconfigured web image search from a tappable error path into a
+  disabled/clear setup state. `Find image` still requires
+  `SAVI_IMAGE_SEARCH_BASE_URL` and the Pexels proxy to be configured.
